00:58:03.820 --> 00:58:08.070
damp the system on this
side, the longer-lived

00:58:08.070 --> 00:58:11.260
is the initial state.

00:58:11.260 --> 00:58:12.280
But it's trivial.

00:58:12.280 --> 00:58:13.610
It's just Fermi's Golden Rule.

00:58:13.610 --> 00:58:16.760
When you couple into a
